Files:
------

README		This file

TODO		Wish list of features to add, things to fix, big and small

include		Include file for all classes

mdwlib          Utility library 1 (c code developed by MDW)

numerical       Utility library 2 (vector class, Gaussian integration
		developed by MDW)

libsrnd		Utility library 3 (random number classes, GNU string class,
		mostly part of the old libg++, no longer maintained by gcc
		folks)

src		Source for nbody code


Compile hints:
--------------

Run: 

libtoolize
aclocal -I m4
autoheader
automake -a
automake
autoconf

And then configure using the following:

./configure --with-vtk-version=6.3 --prefix=/home/someuser --with-boost-libdir=/usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu LDFLAGS=-lmpi --with-vtk-lib-suffix=6.3 --with-dsmc=yes

When configuring alter /home/someuser in the above command to your desired prefix.
Finally run make:

make LDFLAGS="-L." CXXFLAGS="-O3 -DOMPI_SKIP_MPICXX" CFLAGS="-O3" NVCC_EXTRA="-O3" -j16
make install

For checking/verification:

<same>
make CFLAGS="-DDEBUG" CXXFLAGS="-DDEBUG" 

For debugging:

<same>
make CFLAGS="-g -DDEBUG" CXXFLAGS="-g -DDEBUG" 


For sequence checking:

<same>
make CFLAGS="-DSEQCHECK" CXXFLAGS="-DSEQCHECK" 


For dmalloc checking:

<same>
make CFLAGS="-DUSE_MALLOC" CXXFLAGS="-DUSE_DMALLOC" LDFLAG=


To compile with sequence and dmalloc
